== Access ==
* 3.6 km from the {{ill|Hashie Smart Interchange|ja|波志江スマートインターチェンジ|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Kita-Kantō Expressway|ja|北関東自動車道|12=draft}} (10 minutes by car).
* 5 km from the {{ill|Isesaki Interchange|ja|伊勢崎インターチェンジ|12=draft}} on the Kita-Kantō Expressway (10 minutes by car).
* 10 minutes by taxi from {{ill|Ōgo Station|ja|大胡駅|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Jōmō Electric Railway|ja|上毛電気鉄道|12=draft}}.
* 20 minutes by taxi from {{ill|Isesaki Station|ja|伊勢崎駅|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Ryōmō Line|ja|両毛線|12=draft}}.

