== Features == The park includes: * {{ill|Ōmuro Kofun Group (Maebashi)|ja|大室古墳群 (前橋市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōmuro Kofun Group (Maebashi)|qq=}} * {{ill|Umeki Ruins|ja|梅木遺跡|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Umeki Ruins|qq=}} (remains of a clan mansion) * Folk House Garden - featuring the {{ill|Former Sekine Family Residence|ja|旧関根家住宅|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Former Sekine Family Residence|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (a Maebashi City-designated Important Cultural Property) and ancient dwellings.
