== Access == * 3.6 km from the {{ill|Hashie Smart Interchange|ja|波志江スマートインターチェンジ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hashie Smart Interchange|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 波志江パーキングエリア}} on the [[:en:Kita-Kantō Expressway|Kita-Kantō Expressway]] (10 minutes by car). * 5 km from the {{ill|Isesaki Interchange|ja|伊勢崎インターチェンジ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isesaki Interchange|qq=}} on the Kita-Kantō Expressway (10 minutes by car). * 10 minutes by taxi from [[:en:Ōgo Station|Ōgo Station]] on the {{ill|Jōmō Electric Railway|ja|上毛電気鉄道|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōmō Electric Railway|qq=}}. * 20 minutes by taxi from [[:en:Isesaki Station|Isesaki Station]] on the [[:en:Ryōmō Line|Ryōmō Line]].
